{"tid":1311323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「不分化不割蓆」進化版，試著說「普選見」","createTime":"2019-07-13T06:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T04:27:53.000Z","uid":28451,"like":86,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6526435d740d7cda0055caf5baa5ce45b28c1108","tid":1311323,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:27:49.000Z","msg":"中共開始用「群眾鬥群眾」嘅方法入侵<br />\n依家個個post都係捉鬼，好多明明係同路人<br />\n13拳事件，我自己都唔同意，起碼都要擋<br />\n但俾左子彈就用，起碼佢做左文宣材料<br />\n我地唔鼓勵用身體擋拳頭，但唔係屌同路人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「不分化不割蓆」只可以表現團結<br />\n但呢個口號冇表示到任何訴求，結果係失晒方和<br />\n逆向思考，在沒有「普選」嘅前提下，所有爭論都係冇意義<br />\n因為我地嘅爭論係唔會有結局，民意成為唔到選票<br />\n冇投票權嘅民意只會內鬥，只會變成自己人打自己人<br />\n所以最重要係普選，有普選先有爭論嘅空間<br />\n<br />\n在「普選」嘅大前提下，就算法輪功都好，所有意見都應該connect<br />\n<br />\n「不分化不割蓆」要進化<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">普選見</span></span>"},{"pid":"ac0cbd94481741976f29d5b32d0bc28ee347dfff","tid":1311323,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2691c0a1e70510af3b8a65073fa7c6e968866ff1","tid":1311323,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:30:11.000Z","msg":"普選見"},{"pid":"5cbb49abe492042ba8e015584c14c0330f49ca99","tid":1311323,"uid":28451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:31:37.000Z","msg":"下次同fd食飯，臨別試著說「普選見」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737a901ce187a93292b70a11100c106d5d25a3d9","tid":1311323,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:32:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8ca63a3a393d511f2720ef16182681227d037320","tid":1311323,"uid":28451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"737a901ce187a93292b70a11100c106d5d25a3d9","tid":1311323,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:32:54.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2